Adobe replacements:

Photoshop - GIMP, Draw

Illustrator - KRITA, Inkscape

Animate - Pencil, Blender, Draw (https://www.pencil2d.org/, https://www.blender.org/, https://app.diagrams.net/)

After effects - Natron, blender, wax (https://natrongithub.github.io/, https://www.blender.org/, https://wax.en.softonic.com/)

Premiere pro - Shotcut, Openshot, Kdenlive (https://shotcut.org/, https://www.openshot.org/, https://kdenlive.org/en/)

InDesign - Scribus (https://wiki.scribus.net/canvas/Download)
